  "id": "RAW_8d78f7",
  "title": "用 Gemini 2.5 Pro 构建富交互 Web 应用",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/build-rich-interactive-web-apps-with-an-updated-gemini-25-pro/",
  "date": "2025-05-06 15:11:28",
  "author": "Tulsee Doshi",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-05-06T15:11:28.726669+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"pnvzv\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today we're releasing early access to <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/pro/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview</a> (I/O edition), an updated version of 2.5 Pro that has significantly improved capabilities for coding, especially building compelling interactive web apps. We were going to release this update at <a href=\"http://io.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google I/O</a> in a couple weeks, but based on the overwhelming enthusiasm for this model, we wanted to get it in your hands sooner so people can start building.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"54mmg\">This builds on the overwhelmingly positive feedback to Gemini 2.5 Pro’s coding and multimodal reasoning capabilities. Beyond UI-focused development, these improvements extend to other coding tasks such as code transformation, code editing and developing complex agentic workflows.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"A vibrant green fern frond is shown in close-up, with a blurred background suggesting a natural setting. To the right, a digital, code-based representation of the same fern appears as a stippled green outline against a white background, illustrating a transformation of natural form into a digital interpretation.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Nature to code 1\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/nature-to-code-1.mp4\" section-header=\"Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"A vibrant green fern frond is shown in close-up, with a blurred background suggesting a natural setting. To the right, a digital, code-based representation of the same fern appears as a stippled green outline against a white background, illustrating a transformation of natural form into a digital interpretation.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/nature-to-code-1.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/nature-to-code-1.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"ebyy3\"><a href=\"https://g.co/gemini/share/5be8ec4c17d9\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">See the result of this prompt in the Gemini app.</a></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"pnvzv\">With these enhanced capabilities, 2.5 Pro now leads on the <a href=\"https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WebDev Arena Leaderboard</a>, surpassing the previous version by +147 Elo points. This leaderboard measures human preference for a model’s ability to build aesthetically pleasing and functional web apps. It also continues to build on its strong foundation in native multimodality and long context; it has state-of-the-art performance in video understanding, with a score of 84.8% on the VideoMME benchmark.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"4\" thumbnail-alt=\"With improved video understanding and complete UI, the updated Gemini 2.5 Pro model delivers a more functional experience than the previous simple example.\" video-id=\"6lNuSuyv6RQ\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"6lNuSuyv6RQ\" data-index-id=\"4\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6lNuSuyv6RQ/default.webp\" alt=\"With improved video understanding and complete UI, the updated Gemini 2.5 Pro model delivers a more functional experience than the previous simple example.\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6lNuSuyv6RQ/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6lNuSuyv6RQ/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\">\n        <uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\">\n         <!---->\n         <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button--active\" role=\"presentation\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250918-1745#yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component>\n        <uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \">\n         <!---->\n         <svg aria-label=\"Video Title \" class=\"icon uni-article-video__play-button\" role=\"img\">\n          <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250918-1745#yt_video_play_button\"></use>\n         </svg>\n        </uni-icon-component>\n        <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\">\n          <!---->\n          <svg class=\"icon uni-article-video__duration-icon\" role=\"presentation\">\n           <use href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20250918-1745#yt_video_duration\"></use>\n          </svg>\n         </uni-icon-component>\n         <span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"sti8t\"><a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/app/apps/bundled/video-to-learning-app?showPreview=true\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Check out the Video to Learning app on AI Studio.</a></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-pull-quote content-style=\"block\" quote=\"&quot;We're excited about the latest Gemini 2.5 Pro, which builds on its already strong real-world coding capabilities. We're observing internally that the new model has a significant reduction in its failure to call tools, an improvement we believe our users will find makes 2.5 Pro even more effective than before in Cursor.&quot;\" section-header=\"Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro\" author-image-regular=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Cursor-Logo-1-Square.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" author-image-retina=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Cursor-Logo-1-Square.max-96x96.format-webp.webp\" author-name=\"Michael Truell\" author-role=\"CEO, Cursor, an AI coding tool\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"presentation\" class=\" uni-pull-quote uni-pull-quote--block-style \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Pull Quote&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__wrapper\">\n     <p class=\" uni-pull-quote__text uni-pull-quote__text--long \"><!--?lit$8886419961$-->\"We're excited about the latest Gemini 2.5 Pro, which builds on its already strong real-world coding capabilities. We're observing internally that the new model has a significant reduction in its failure to call tools, an improvement we believe our users will find makes 2.5 Pro even more effective than before in Cursor.\"</p>\n     <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n     <div class=\"uni-pull-quote__author\">\n      <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n      <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n      <div class=\"authors-byline-container\">\n       <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n       <!---->\n       <div class=\"author-byline\">\n        <a class=\"author-byline__link author-byline__link--disabled\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$8886419961$--><!--?lit$8886419961$--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__image-container\">\n          <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (min-width: 601px) 50vw\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Cursor-Logo-1-Square.max-48x48.format-webp.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Cursor-Logo-1-Square.max-48x48.format-webp.webp, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Cursor-Logo-1-Square.max-96x96.format-webp.webp 2x\">\n         </div> \n         <!--?--> \n         <div class=\"author-byline__info\">\n          <p class=\"author-byline__info-name uni-author-name\"><!--?lit$8886419961$-->Michael Truell</p>\n          <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n          <div class=\"author-byline__info-title uni-author-info\">\n           <!--?lit$8886419961$-->\n           CEO, Cursor, an AI coding tool\n          </div>\n         </div></a>\n       </div>\n       <!---->\n      </div>\n      <!--?-->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </section>\n  </uni-pull-quote>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Build rich, interactive web apps with an updated Gemini 2.5 Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"pnvzv\">Developers can start building with this updated Gemini 2.5 Pro in the Gemini API via <a href=\"http://aistudio.google.com/app/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-2.5-pro-preview-05-06\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a> and <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>. It’s also available for users in the<a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"> Gemini app</a>, powering features like <a href=\"https://gemini.google.com/canvas\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Canvas</a>, and enabling anyone to vibe code and build interactive web apps with a single prompt.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 提前发布了编码能力显著提升的 Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview 版，主打交互式 Web 应用构建，并在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上取得领先。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 提前发布了编码能力显著提升的 Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview 版，主打交互式 Web 应用构建，并在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上取得领先。",
  "summary": "Google DeepMind 发布了 Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview 版，该版本在编码能力上有了显著提升，尤其是在构建引人入胜的交互式 Web 应用方面，仅需单条指令即可完成。此更新建立在 Gemini 2.5 Pro 在编码和多模态推理能力方面获得的积极反馈之上。除了 UI 开发，这些改进还扩展到其他编码任务，如代码转换、代码编辑和开发复杂代理工作流。该模型在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上超越了之前的版本，并在视频理解方面取得了最先进的性能。开发者可以通过 Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI 中的 Gemini API 开始使用此更新。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 2.5 Pro 在 Web 应用构建方面能力显著提升，在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上提升了 +147 Elo points",
      "explanation": "该模型在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上超过之前的版本，提升了 +147 Elo points，表明其在构建美观且功能强大的 Web 应用方面有显著进步。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新版本扩展了编码任务的应用范围",
      "explanation": "除了 UI 开发，Gemini 2.5 Pro 还在代码转换、代码编辑和开发复杂代理工作流等编码任务中表现出改进。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 2.5 Pro 在视频理解方面表现出色",
      "explanation": "该模型在 VideoMME 基准测试中获得了 84.8% 的评分，表明其在视频理解方面具有领先水平。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "凭借这些增强的功能，2.5 Pro 现在在 WebDev Arena 排行榜上处于领先地位，超过了之前的版本 +147 Elo points。",
    "我们对最新的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 感到兴奋，它建立在其已经强大的真实世界编码能力之上。",
    "我们内部观察到，新模型在调用工具失败的情况显著减少，我们相信我们的用户会发现，与之前在 Cursor 中相比，2.5 Pro 更加有效。"
  ],
